RIT Capital Partners PLC


            
            RIT Capital Partners plc is an investment trust. It invests in diversified international portfolio. The company was founded by Jacob Rothschild in 1988 and is headquartered in London, United Kingdom.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 
   






   



























